    "description_long": "This object is a vintage-style radio receiver with a rectangular body finished in a dark, reddish-brown wood grain. The front panel features a metallic speaker grille on the left, a large circular tuning dial with a metallic finish and frequency markings, and two smaller control knobs below it. A stylized metallic logo is present on the lower left of the front panel. The back side has a vented metal panel with a power input, a green button, and a USB port, suggesting modern connectivity. The sides and top are smooth, uninterrupted wood grain, giving it a classic, retro appearance.",
